      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly i dont even know why im typing this. everything is just gone. the company, the funding, the reputation... i owe people money i can never pay back. i just saw a photo of my parents and i felt sick. they think i'm a success and now i'm just this massive, walking embarrassment to them. i feel like a ghost already.",
