      "content": "I hear the absolute darkness in this moment, and while the feeling that there is no path forward is incredibly heavy, the desire to end your life is often a symptom of overwhelming pain rather than a true desire to cease existing. Your years of hard work built a foundation that cannot be instantly erased by market shifts, and your worth is tied to your struggle, not your financial success. Please, consider speaking with a crisis counselor immediately because they can offer a lifeline when the person in the mirror feels like a stranger.",
